Entries.default: "The culling is complete. We have at long last the three strongest packs of this season."
"And now, they shall fight! The pack that remains will be the Champions of the Hunt!"
"For the glory of the Crucible - in the name of Toamowhai - may the strongest, swiftest, smartest pack triumph."
"The hunt concludes. Raise your voices in glory to these, the Champions of the Hunt!"
"Congratulations, Watcher! May you defend the title for as long as your strength deserves it!"

In tones excited, surprised, and all things in the middle, your name roars from the crowd, echoing from every direction.
"When you tire of the adulation, return to the Pool of Memories. Humaire will see to your coronation."
